			<h3>Can design make the world a better place?</h3>
			<p> Subforum is an award-winning, multidisciplinary design and research group. Subforum was founded in 2012 to help address the gulf between academic research, applied practice, and “industry” in general. We believe that all forms of design must be done with a deep sense of responsibility to elevate, rather than detract from, the human experience. We exist to improve our environment, ecosystem, and experience through design. </p>

