			<h3>Who is Subforum?</h3>
			<p> We are a small team of designers and researchers spanning the industrial, architectural, and interaction design disciplines. The group is comprised of three topic teams and a small core team. Topic teams are dedicated to researching, understanding, and communicating findings about issues of critical importance in design. At present, Subforum’s topic teams focus on remote collaboration, distraction, and routines. The core team exists to orchestrate the group as a whole and to support the efforts of the topic teams. Contact us at info@subforum.org to learn more about turning design insights into world improving tools.</p>
